NK041(di)054:0: bkra shis don kun grub pa'i dbyangs snyan zhes bya ba /
NK041(di)054:2: chos dbyings nam mkha'i khyon kun yongs khyab pa'i //
NK041(di)054:3: rab 'byams rtsa ba gsum gyi lha yi tshogs //
NK041(di)054:4: til gyi gong bu bzhin du bzhugs pa yi //
NK041(di)054:5: rgyal ba'i dbang po rnams kyis dgongs pa mdzad //
NK041(di)054:6: yum rnams rin chen bum pas dbang bskur zhing //
NK041(di)054:7: sems dpa'i tshogs kyi bkra shis me tog 'thor //
NK041(di)054:8: lha rnams kun gyis rdo rje'i glu dbyangs len //
NK041(di)054:9: khro bo'i tshogs kyis bgegs rnams pha mthar bskrad //
NK041(di)054:10: 'jig rten skyong ba'i tshogs kyis mchod cing bstod //
NK041(di)054:11: kun kyang dge bzhin bkra shis dpal yon kun //
NK041(di)054:12: deng 'dir mngon par stsol ba nyid gyur las //
NK041(di)054:13: bkra shis rab mchog bdag gis brjod par bya //
NK041(di)054:14: dga' rab sh+r+ai seng pad+ma thod phreng rtsal //
NK041(di)054:15: grub mchog brgyad dang rje 'bangs nyi shu lnga //
NK041(di)054:16: gter ston brgya rtsa bka' gter dag snang brgyud //
NK041(di)054:17: rig 'dzin bla ma'i tshogs kyi bkra shis des //
NK041(di)054:18: deng 'dir mi mthun rgud pa kun zhi nas //
NK041(di)054:19: mthun rkyen tshe bsod bde legs gong du 'phel //
NK041(di)054:20: ji ltar bsam pa yid bzhin lhun gyis grub //
NK041(di)054:21: phun tshogs dpal yon rgyas pa'i bkra shis shog /
NK041(di)054:22: gdod ma'i mgon po rigs lnga gangs chen mtsho //
NK041(di)054:23: ston pa bcu gnyis sangs rgyas stong la sogs //
NK041(di)054:24: mkha' khyab phyogs bcu'i zhing na bzhugs pa yi //
NK041(di)054:25: dus gsum bde bar bshegs pa'i bkra shis des //
NK041(di)054:26: deng 'dir mthun rkyen ji ltar phun tshogs rigs brgya rigs lnga rigs gsum rigs mchog gcig /
NK041(di)054:27: sgrub pa sde brgyad bdud 'dul khro bo bcu //
NK041(di)054:28: zhi dang khro tshul sgyu 'phrul d+r+wa ba'i gar //
NK041(di)054:29: rab 'byams yi dam lha yi bkra shis des //
NK041(di)054:30: deng 'dir mthun rkyen ji ltar phun tshogs sde snod gsum dang rgyud sde chen po drug /
NK041(di)054:31: rgyud lung man ngag bka' gter dag snang sogs //
NK041(di)054:32: rgyal ba rig 'dzin brgyud pa'i thugs kyi bcud //
NK041(di)054:33: lung rtogs dam pa'i chos kyi bkra shis des //
NK041(di)054:34: deng 'dir mthun rkyen ji ltar phun tshogs nye ba'i sras mchog brgyad dang sems ma brgyad //
NK041(di)054:35: skal bzang sems dpa' stong la sogs pa yi //
NK041(di)054:36: phyogs bcu dus gsum dag gi rgyal ba'i sras //
NK041(di)054:37: yon tan rgya mtsho rnams kyi bkra shis des //
NK041(di)054:38: deng 'dir mthun rkyen ji ltar phun tshogs rdo rje phag mo rigs lnga'i d+aa ki n+ai //
NK041(di)054:39: mtsho rgyal la sogs thugs kyi dgyes sde lnga //
NK041(di)054:40: gnas yul zhing gi dpa' bo rnal 'byor ma //
NK041(di)054:41: dpal ldan mkha' 'gro'i tshogs kyi bkra shis des //
NK041(di)054:42: deng 'dir mthun rkyen ji ltar phun tshogs sde dpon sum cu dregs chen bco brgyad dang //
NK041(di)054:43: tshangs dbang khyab 'jug brgya byin rgyal chen sogs //
NK041(di)054:44: dus gsum rgyal ba'i phrin las bka' skyong ba //
NK041(di)054:45: rdo rje'i chos skyong tshogs kyi bkra shis des //
NK041(di)054:46: deng 'dir mthun rkyen ji ltar phun tshogs bstan 'dzin zhabs brtan bshad sgrub bstan pa dar //
NK041(di)054:47: bstan pa'i sbyin bdag rnams dang 'gro ba kun //
NK041(di)054:48: bde skyid gong 'phel chos ldan bsam don 'grub //
NK041(di)054:49: sa gsum dpal dang ldan pa'i bkra shis shog /
NK041(di)054:50: snang srid rnam dag bde pa chen po la //
NK041(di)054:51: mi shis rgud pa ye nas mi mnga' ba'i //
NK041(di)054:52: bden pa de yis mkha' khyab 'gro ba kun //
NK041(di)054:53: rang byung ye shes rtogs pa'i bkra shis shog /
NK041(di)054:54: mnyam nyid ngang nas phyogs dus 'gro kun la //
NK041(di)054:55: phan dang bde ba'i phrin las lhun gyis grub //
NK041(di)054:56: rtag khyab mtshungs med bkra shis dpal gyi mchog /
NK041(di)054:57: deng 'dir mngon du 'gyur ba'i bkra shis shog /
NK041(di)054:58: sa gsum dbang byed srid gsum bran du 'khol //
NK041(di)054:59: phyogs las rnam rgyal snang srid zil gnon pa'i //
NK041(di)054:60: o rgyan rig 'dzin brgyud pa'i ring lugs gang //
NK041(di)054:61: phyogs dus kun tu rgyas pa'i bkra shis shog /
NK041(di)054:62: ces pa'ang rab tshes me sprel 'od 'bar gdong pa
NK041(di)054:63: bzang po'i zla 11tshes gza' skar sogs dus kyi cha
NK041(di)054:64: shin tu dge bar sgrub khang 'chi med mchog grub
NK041(di)054:65: gling du mi pham 'jam dpal dgyes pa'i rdo rje'i
NK041(di)054:66: blo mtsho las byung ba nor bu'i gter chen po
NK041(di)054:67: bkra shis dang dge legs mi zad pa gong nas
NK041(di)054:68: gong du 'phel bar byed pa 'di snga 'gyur ba
NK041(di)054:69: rnams kyi dpal du gnas pa de phyir spel bar
